```

With aggregate preservation:
```verilog
module Foo(
  input                                          clock,
                                                 reset,
  input  struct packed {logic a; logic b; }[0:0] a,
  output struct packed {logic a; logic b; }[0:0] b);

  wire struct packed {logic a; logic b; }[0:0] bar_w = a;
  assign b = a;
endmodule
```

